## Request notification code 

> Example Email Request

```shell
curl "<%= config.host %>/client/notification/request-code" \
  -H "<%= config.auth %>" \
  -d '{
    "clientId": "56e1ddbd1a05319bc198d36f",
    "destination": "sean.hill@notification.com"
  }'
```

> Example Phone Number Request

```shell
curl "<%= config.host %>/client/notification/request-code" \
  -H "<%= config.auth %>" \
  -d '{
    "clientId": "56e1ddbd1a05319bc198d36f",
    "destination": "1234567890"
  }'
```

> Example Response

```json
{
  "success": true
}
```

Requests a verification code to be sent to a specified `destination`.

### HTTP Request

`POST <%= config.host %>/client/notification/request-code`

### Arguments

Parameter | Description
----- | -----------
`clientId` | ID of the client to send the verification code to.
`destination` | A valid email address or US phone number.

### Returns

Returns an object with a `success` if the code was successfully sent to the `destination`. Returns an error otherwise.
